      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '14.1. The Employee (hereafter referred to as "Miner") agrees to fulfill
    a daily minimum extraction Quota, determined solely by Regional Management. Failure
    to meet the daily Quota will result in immediate termination of this contract
    and abandonment in the lower shafts.


    14.2. Upon successful completion of
    the daily Quota, the Corporation shall graciously allocate thirty percent (30%)
    of the total daily gross value to the Miner''s personal bank for upgrade purchases
    and leisure.


    14.3. The remaining seventy percent (70%) shall be retained
    by the Corporation to cover operational costs, equipment leasing, headlamp battery
    recycling, and mandatory morale fees.


    By signing below, you acknowledge
    that you belong to the Corporation for the next 15 days, or until structural
    collapse, whichever comes first.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
